&D              rt ra si
@D              ...... rt:5 ra:5 si:s16                 &D

# If a prefix is allowed, decode with default values.
&PLS_D          rt ra si:int64_t r:bool
@PLS_D          ...... rt:5 ra:5 si:s16                 &PLS_D r=0

### Fixed-Point Arithmetic Instructions

ADDI            001110 ..... ..... ................     @PLS_D
ADDIS           001111 ..... ..... ................     @D
